room_title: Escape room "Con Artist" by Escape Room Virginia Beach in Virginia Beach
room_address: 408 Investors Place, Suite 107 Virginia Beach, VA 23452
room_description: Interested in buying a famous painting, you go to a studio that claims to have originals for sale. When you arrive and find that the seller isn’t there, you try to leave, but find that the door locked behind you. Something feels off, but you aren’t sure why. Find another way out before the seller returns and you find the truth behind the uneasy feeling.
